  "body_sections": [
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Weighted FLOP cost of an SVD (FMA=2, leading order)."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "inline": [
                    {
                      "kind": "text",
                      "text": "values only (with_vectors=False):        2*a*b^2 + 2*b^3\nthin U, V (full_matrices=False):         6*a*b^2 + 20*b^3\nfull U (full_matrices=True and m != n):  4*a^2*b + 22*b^3"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "term_inline": [
                {
                  "kind": "text",
                  "text": "Full decomposition ("
                },
                {
                  "kind": "code",
                  "text": "k is None"
                },
                {
                  "kind": "text",
                  "text": "), with a = max(m, n), b = min(m, n):"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "definition_list"
        },
        {
          "raw_kind": "system_message",
          "raw_text": "<string>:5: (WARNING/2) Definition list ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent.",
          "type": "raw_block"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": "Constants from the 2026-06 evidence audit (LAPACK dgesdd + G&VL 4e \u00a78.6);\nsee docs/reference/cost-model.md."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "inline": [
                    {
                      "kind": "text",
                      "text": "min(4*m*n*k, economy)"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "term_inline": [
                {
                  "kind": "text",
                  "text": "Top-k truncated SVD ("
                },
                {
                  "kind": "code",
                  "text": "1 <= k < min(m, n)"
                },
                {
                  "kind": "text",
                  "text": "):"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "definition_list"
        },
        {
          "raw_kind": "system_message",
          "raw_text": "<string>:10: (WARNING/2) Definition list ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent.",
          "type": "raw_block"
        },
        {
          "inline": [
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "4*m*n*k"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " is the verified leading-order cost of a rank-k randomized SVD\n(Halko-Martinsson-Tropp; two passes over A, Theta(m*n*k)). flopscope bills\nthis standard truncated-algorithm cost even though the reference\nimplementation computes the full economy SVD and slices \u2014 it bills the\ntextbook cost of the operation (like matmul), not literal BLAS work.\nValues-only is NOT leading-order cheaper for the truncated case (unlike the\nfull case). "
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "k >= min(m, n)"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": " bills the economy cost; the full_matrices\nfull-U premium applies only to the full decomposition ("
            },
            {
              "kind": "code",
              "text": "k is None"
            },
            {
              "kind": "text",
              "text": ").\nSee docs/reference/cost-model.md."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Extended Summary"
    },
